title: Rockin it with Rocky Patel!
itunes:title: Rockin it with Rocky Patel!
description: Today on The Cigar Authority we're ROCKING at Two Guys Smoke Shop in Salem with Cigarlebrity  ROCKY PATEL. Rocky joins Dave Garofalo, Mr Jonathan and Chuck Morrison where we ask, 'What's the best RP Vintage Cigar?' 1999 Connecticut, 1990 or 1992? It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority!
